---
const zones = [
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Barrio Dalvian' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Chacras de Coria' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Vistalba' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Ciudad de Mendoza' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Luján de Cuyo' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Maipú' },
];
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark" id="mendoza">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
      <span class="inline-block text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4">Presencia Local</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Especialistas en Dalvian y Gran Mendoza
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        Entendemos el ritmo de vida de Mendoza. Por eso, nuestro servicio de sueroterapia a domicilio está diseñado para integrarse perfectamente en tu rutina sin que tengas que desplazarte.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Zone tags -->
    <div class="stagger-group flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-14">
      {zones.map((zone) => (
        <div class="stagger-item flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/8 dark:bg-primary/15 border border-primary/15 text-primary text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary/15 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" style="font-size: 16px; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400;">{zone.icon}</span>
          {zone.name}
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Map placeholder -->
    <div class="animate-on-scroll aspect-[21/9] w-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-surface-dark-2 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 relative group">
      <!-- Subtle background grid -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 dark:opacity-20"
        style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(95,108,90,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(95,108,90,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"
      ></div>

      <!-- Radial gradient overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 via-transparent to-primary/5 pointer-events-none"></div>

      <!-- Center content -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary opacity-20 text-8xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 100;">map</span>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark px-6 py-3.5 rounded-full shadow-xl border border-primary/10 dark:border-primary/20 flex items-center gap-2.5 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105">
          <div class="relative">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400;">location_on</span>
            <span class="absolute -top-0.5 -right-0.5 flex h-2 w-2">
              <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-60"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 text-sm">Servicio en toda Mendoza</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats row -->
    <div class="stagger-group grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="stagger-item text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary mb-1">15 km</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Radio de cobertura</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stagger-item text-center border-x border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary mb-1">&lt;60 min</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Tiempo de llegada</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stagger-item text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary mb-1">7 días</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Disponibilidad semanal</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
